      <title>法国提前选举首轮投票率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/french-voter-turnout-soars-in-first-round-of-snap-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国提前举行的立法选举第一轮投票率达到本世纪最高，极右翼国民联盟在选举中占据主导地位。]]></description>
